{
  "stem": "3874.1",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And there were a lot of children who went to England on children's transports-- to Belgium, the Netherlands.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And my parents tried to get me onto these transports-- my brother and myself.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And through the the Austrian, the [GERMAN] the Jewish [GERMAN], found out about transports that France was taking some kids, and tried to get my brother and myself onto this-- onto a children's transport to France.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I have the paper-- I have the application still that shows-- I have the application from-- from 1939, the application to-- for me to go to France.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "My-- now, my brother at the time was 13, I was 10 and a half.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "The organization would only take children up to the age of 13.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Once you're 13, they deemed you're just too old.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Excuse me.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So consequently, my brother didn't get out.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I got on a transport into France.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I want you to tell us a little bit, if you would, about what you remember actually leaving, and what your parents told you, and your response to leaving.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I don't want you to rush through that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, OK.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, several things.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Number one, my parents-- the idea was that they were going to send me out and my brother out-- of course, he didn't go-- but they were going to get visas, follow me, pick me up in France, and eventually would go to the United States-- someplace.",
      "word_count": 47
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I also remember, well, actually, the night before I left, I did several things.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "One of them, I was very happy for.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "One of them is still on my conscience as-- it followed me around for a long, long time.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
